      <title>加拿大要求邮政工人在罢工一个月后重返工作岗位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-13/canada-orders-postal-workers-back-to-job-after-month-long-strike</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大政府要求独立劳工委员会命令 55,000 名加拿大邮政公司员工复工，此举有望结束在繁忙假日季节中断邮政服务近一个月的罢工。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-13/canada-orders-postal-workers-back-to-job-after-month-long-strike</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Dec 2024 16:42:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>据称 Textor 正在考虑将 Eagle Football 的股份出售给 Sportsbank</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-13/textor-said-to-weigh-selling-eagle-football-stake-to-sportsbank</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，足球俱乐部最活跃的投资者之一约翰·特克斯特 (John Textor) 正在讨论将其在 Eagle Football Holdings Ltd. 投资公司中的股份出售给 Sportsbank 的可能性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-13/textor-said-to-weigh-selling-eagle-football-stake-to-sportsbank</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Dec 2024 16:27:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>受中国金属限制影响，力拓计划在加拿大建设镓工厂</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-13/rio-tinto-eyes-gallium-plant-in-canada-after-china-metals-curb</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在中国禁止向美国出口用于制造半导体、智能手机和电动汽车的稀有金属镓之后，力拓集团正在寻找在加拿大生产镓的方法。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-13/rio-tinto-eyes-gallium-plant-in-canada-after-china-metals-curb</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Dec 2024 16:25:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>应对钻石需求低迷</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-13/fighting-the-dulling-demand-for-diamonds-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[实验室培育钻石的兴起正在颠覆珠宝行业。全球最大的钻石生产商戴比尔斯不得不全线降价 10% 以上。在线珠宝商 Angara 的首席执行官 Ankur Daga 参加了彭博公开交易，讨论该行业如何度过几十年来最严重、最持久的低迷之一。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-13/fighting-the-dulling-demand-for-diamonds-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Dec 2024 16:06:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>迈克·威尔逊表示明年可能会出现调整</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-13/wilson-says-there-could-be-a-correction-next-year-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根士丹利首席美国股票策略师迈克·威尔逊表示，2025 年上半年可能会出现市场调整，但平均股价可能不会下跌那么多。他在“彭博未平仓合约”上。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-13/wilson-says-there-could-be-a-correction-next-year-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Dec 2024 15:29:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>财政部长称欧盟债券可能对荷兰债务构成威胁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-13/eu-bonds-could-be-a-threat-to-dutch-debt-treasury-chief-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[荷兰财政部负责人表示，如果指数提供商将欧盟债券重新归类为主权证券，则可能对荷兰债券构成威胁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-13/eu-bonds-could-be-a-threat-to-dutch-debt-treasury-chief-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Dec 2024 15:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日元创六月以来最长连跌纪录，因押注日本央行维持利率不变</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-13/yen-set-for-longest-losing-streak-since-june-on-bets-boj-to-hold</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易员押注日本央行下周将不会加息，日元兑美元汇率创下了自六月以来最长的连续下跌走势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-13/yen-set-for-longest-losing-streak-since-june-on-bets-boj-to-hold</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Dec 2024 10:26:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊朗和俄罗斯制裁可能缓解供应过剩前景，油价上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-12/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-december-13</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于地缘政治紧张局势不断升温，且对俄罗斯和伊朗实施制裁的可能性抵消了明年供应过剩的预测，油价上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-12/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-december-13</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Dec 2024 23:30:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>科技股从纪录高位回落，标普指数表现挣扎：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-12/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纳斯达克 100 指数本周第二次创下历史新高，但随后回吐了 1% 以上的涨幅，原因是博通公司 (Broadcom Inc.) 股价飙升，带动整个芯片技术板块上涨。美国国债下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-12/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Dec 2024 22:36:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
